  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065560/extras/7d5b059688600fb35601bff197a7acb1.avif?t=1750429973\" width=131 height=100 /></span><br><br><strong>A Short wandering & running adventure inside of your own nightmare. </strong><br>Everyone has already dreamed of being in an unknown place, strangely free in their movements, it was all fun and games... until \"They\" appears.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065560/extras/ca3c445f6f1b8c70be649d3533c5892b.poster.avif?t=1750429973\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065560/extras/ca3c445f6f1b8c70be649d3533c5892b.webm?t=1750429973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065560/extras/ca3c445f6f1b8c70be649d3533c5892b.mp4?t=1750429973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>>_CONCEPT :</strong><br><br>Acanthoceras is a fast-paced Horror/Parkour mixup where your only option is to repeat a cycle of fear, search, and run, <br>in the hope of escaping the nightmares chasing you.<br><br>The game lets you wandering in a abandoned hospital littered with puppet pieces. <br>A few papers on the floor are your only way to figure out what's going on.<br>You're free to move, run, jump, and slide...but will that be enough to escape?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065560/extras/e6240ed986f2e77aa8c6c207fea6963d.poster.avif?t=1750429973\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065560/extras/e6240ed986f2e77aa8c6c207fea6963d.webm?t=1750429973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065560/extras/e6240ed986f2e77aa8c6c207fea6963d.mp4?t=1750429973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Good luck and... Have fun.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065560/extras/8ba2fccbb384174fb2fd31f29bc556d2.avif?t=1750429973\" width=80 height=80 /></span><br><br>\"Welcome back old friend...<br>To come back here every night, did you miss us so much ?<br>Oh there is no need to answer...<br><br>You'd better start running don't you think ?\"<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065560/extras/8ba2fccbb384174fb2fd31f29bc556d2.avif?t=1750429973\" width=80 height=80 /></span><br><br><strong>>_TECH & HELP :</strong><br><br>    Recommended resolution : 1920 x 1080.<br><br>    Basics Commands :<br>    - WASD / ZQSD  : move around.<br>    - Space : Jump. (Can be charged).<br>    - C / Ctrl : Slide & Crawl.<br>    - Shift : Dash.<br>    - E : Interact.<br><br>    Advenced Commands : <br>    - Double tap direction : Flip.<br>    - Side + Forward on a wall : Wall run.<br><br><strong>>_Cast :</strong><br>    Game - Amaury Hyde.<br>    Music - Tom Morel.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065560/extras/7d5b059688600fb35601bff197a7acb1.avif?t=1750429973\" width=131 height=100 /></span><br><br><strong>A Short wandering & running adventure inside of your own nightmare. </strong><br>Everyone has already dreamed of being in an unknown place, strangely free in their movements, it was all fun and games... until \"They\" appears.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065560/extras/ca3c445f6f1b8c70be649d3533c5892b.poster.avif?t=1750429973\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065560/extras/ca3c445f6f1b8c70be649d3533c5892b.webm?t=1750429973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065560/extras/ca3c445f6f1b8c70be649d3533c5892b.mp4?t=1750429973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>>_CONCEPT :</strong><br><br>Acanthoceras is a fast-paced Horror/Parkour mixup where your only option is to repeat a cycle of fear, search, and run, <br>in the hope of escaping the nightmares chasing you.<br><br>The game lets you wandering in a abandoned hospital littered with puppet pieces. <br>A few papers on the floor are your only way to figure out what's going on.<br>You're free to move, run, jump, and slide...but will that be enough to escape?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065560/extras/e6240ed986f2e77aa8c6c207fea6963d.poster.avif?t=1750429973\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065560/extras/e6240ed986f2e77aa8c6c207fea6963d.webm?t=1750429973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065560/extras/e6240ed986f2e77aa8c6c207fea6963d.mp4?t=1750429973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Good luck and... Have fun.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065560/extras/8ba2fccbb384174fb2fd31f29bc556d2.avif?t=1750429973\" width=80 height=80 /></span><br><br>\"Welcome back old friend...<br>To come back here every night, did you miss us so much ?<br>Oh there is no need to answer...<br><br>You'd better start running don't you think ?\"<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065560/extras/8ba2fccbb384174fb2fd31f29bc556d2.avif?t=1750429973\" width=80 height=80 /></span><br><br><strong>>_TECH & HELP :</strong><br><br>    Recommended resolution : 1920 x 1080.<br><br>    Basics Commands :<br>    - WASD / ZQSD  : move around.<br>    - Space : Jump. (Can be charged).<br>    - C / Ctrl : Slide & Crawl.<br>    - Shift : Dash.<br>    - E : Interact.<br><br>    Advenced Commands : <br>    - Double tap direction : Flip.<br>    - Side + Forward on a wall : Wall run.<br><br><strong>>_Cast :</strong><br>    Game - Amaury Hyde.<br>    Music - Tom Morel.",
